"Configure the data source locally and download the required historical data;"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:6
msgid ""
"使用 `get_history_data()` 或 `get_history_panel()` 获取价格、成交量等基础行情。"
msgstr ""
"Use `get_history_data()` or `get_history_panel()` to obtain basic market data "
"such as prices and trading volume."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:8
msgid "本章将在此基础上，通过一个完整的小例子，演示如何使用 `HistoryPanel`："
msgstr ""
"Building on this, this chapter will use a complete small example to demonstrate "
"how to use `HistoryPanel`: "

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:10
msgid "统一管理多标的、多指标的历史数据；"
msgstr ""
"Unified management of historical data for multiple instruments and multiple "
"indicators;"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:11
msgid "计算收益率、波动率等简单因子；"
msgstr "Calculate simple factors such as returns and volatility;"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:12
