#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:106
msgid "3.1 inplace：原地扩列（减少拷贝）"
msgstr "3.1 inplace: expand columns in place (reduce copying)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:108
msgid ""
"默认情况下，`kline.*` 返回 **新** `HistoryPanel`（不污染原对象）。当你希望在同一"
"个面板上连续追加多列，并减少中间对象时，可以使用 `inplace=True`："
msgstr ""
"By default, `kline.*` returns a **new** `HistoryPanel` (without mutating the "
"original object). When you want to append multiple columns continuously on the "
"same panel and reduce intermediate objects, you can use `inplace=True`:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:117
msgid ""
"提示：当新列名与已有列名冲突时，`kline.*` 会抛出英文 `ValueError`，避免静默覆"
"盖。"
msgstr ""
"Tip: When a new column name conflicts with an existing column name, `kline.*` "
"will raise an English `ValueError` to avoid silent overwriting."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:119
msgid "3.2 第一入口：research_preset（一行拼列 + 直接出图）"
msgstr ""
"3.2 First entry point: research_preset (one-line column chaining + direct "
"plotting)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:121
msgid ""
"如果你希望“拿到数据后立刻得到一张像样的图”，推荐直接使用 `research_preset` 生成"
"官方预设的常用列集合（预设只做显式追加，不在 `plot()` 内隐藏计算）："
msgstr ""
"If you want to “get a decent-looking chart as soon as you have the data”, it’s "
"recommended to use `research_preset` directly to generate the official preset "
"set of commonly used columns (the preset only does explicit appends and does "
"not hide computations inside `plot()`):"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:132
msgid ""
"当输入面板缺少预设所需的输入列时，会抛出英文 `ValueError`，信息包含缺失列列表与"
"补齐建议。"
msgstr ""
"When the input panel is missing the input columns required by the preset, an "
"English `ValueError` will be raised; the message includes the list of missing "
"columns and suggestions on how to fill them in."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:136
msgid "4. 使用 assign 一次派生多列"
msgstr "4. Use assign to derive multiple columns at once"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:138
msgid ""
"在实际研究中，经常需要基于已有列派生出多个新因子，例如价差、比例、缩放后的归一化"
"值等。``HistoryPanel.assign()`` 提供了一次性派生多列的 DSL："
msgstr ""
"In practical research, you often need to derive multiple new factors from "
"existing columns, such as spreads, ratios, scaled normalized values, and so on. "
"``HistoryPanel.assign()`` provides a DSL for deriving multiple columns in one "
"go:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:149
msgid ""
"`assign` 的关键字参数名称即新列名（htype），值可以是接收当前 `HistoryPanel` 的可"
"调用对象，也可以是可广播到 `(M,L)` 的数组或标量；"
msgstr ""
"The keyword argument names of `assign` are the new column names (htype); the "
"values can be callables that take the current `HistoryPanel`, or arrays/scalars "
"that can be broadcast to `(M,L)`;"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:150
msgid "同一次调用内，后面的列可以依赖前面刚新增的列，例如："
msgstr ""
"Within the same call, later columns can depend on columns that were just added "
"earlier, for example:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:159
msgid ""
"默认 `inplace=False`，返回新面板，不修改原对象；当你希望在原面板上原地扩列时，可"
"以使用："
msgstr ""
"By default, `inplace=False`, which returns a new panel without modifying the "
"original object; when you want to expand columns in place on the original "
"panel, you can use:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:165
msgid ""
"提示：与 `hp['col'] = ...` 一样，`assign` 对已有列名采用“覆盖”语义；空面板上调"
"用 `assign` 会抛出英文 `ValueError`。"
msgstr ""
"Tip: Like `hp['col'] = ...`, `assign` uses “overwrite” semantics for existing "
"column names; calling `assign` on an empty panel will raise an English "
"`ValueError`."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:169
msgid "5. 横截面 rank 与 zscore（cs/ts）"
msgstr "5. Cross-sectional rank and zscore (cs/ts)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:171
msgid "多标的研究中常见的两类标准化需求是："
msgstr "In multi-asset research, two common types of standardization needs are:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:173
msgid ""
"**截面（cross-sectional）**：固定某个交易日，对所有股票的因子值做标准化或排名；"
msgstr ""
"**Cross-sectional**: fix a trading day and standardize or rank factor values "
"across all stocks;"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:174
msgid ""
"**时序（time-series rolling）**：固定某只股票，对它自己的历史序列用滚动窗口做标"
"准化。"
msgstr ""
"**Time-series (rolling)**: fix a stock and use a rolling window to standardize "
"its own historical series."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:176
msgid ""
"`HistoryPanel.rank()` 与 `HistoryPanel.zscore()` 提供了这两类最基础变换（仅做变"
"换，不做回归推断）："
msgstr ""
"`HistoryPanel.rank()` and `HistoryPanel.zscore()` provide the most basic "
"transformations of these two types (transformations only, no regression "
"inference):"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:189
msgid ""
"提示：`zscore(method='cs')` 与 `zscore(method='ts')` 语义完全不同，务必显式指定 "
"`method`（并在 `ts` 场景提供 `window`），避免把“截面标准化”误当成“时序标准化”。"
msgstr ""
"Note: `zscore(method='cs')` and `zscore(method='ts')` have completely different "
"semantics. Be sure to explicitly specify `method` (and provide `window` in the "
"`ts` case) to avoid mistaking “cross-sectional standardization” for “time-"
"series standardization”."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:191
msgid "5.5 对齐与重采样（align_to / resample）：避免 silent 错行"
msgstr ""
"5.5 Alignment and resampling (align_to / resample): avoid silent row "
"misalignment"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:193
msgid ""
"当你手里有两块 `HistoryPanel`，想做逐元素运算（比如 `hp_factor / hp_price`、或两"
"面板相减）时，需要特别注意："
msgstr ""
"So when you have two `HistoryPanel`s and want to do element-wise operations "
"(such as `hp_factor / hp_price` or subtracting two panels), you need to pay "
"special attention:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:195
msgid "`HistoryPanel` **不会**在运算符里自动对齐两块面板；"
msgstr ""
"`HistoryPanel` **will not** automatically align two panels inside operators;"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:196
msgid ""
"若 `shares` / `hdates` 不一致，直接拿 `.values` 做 NumPy 运算很容易出现“看起来能"
"算、但其实错行”的结果。"
msgstr ""
"If `shares` / `hdates` are inconsistent, doing NumPy operations directly on "
"`.values` can easily produce results that “seem to compute, but are actually "
"misaligned by rows”."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:198
msgid "因此建议遵循固定流程：**先对齐，再计算**。"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, it’s recommended to follow a fixed workflow: **align first, then "
"compute**."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:207
msgid ""
"=当你需要把日线变成周线/月线等更低频数据时，可用 `resample()`，并**显式**指定每"
"一列的聚合规则（避免语义不明）："
msgstr ""
"=When you need to convert daily data into lower-frequency data such as weekly/"
"monthly, you can use `resample()` and **explicitly** specify the aggregation "
"rule for each column (to avoid unclear semantics):"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:221
msgid ""
"提示：`resample()` 要求 `agg` 覆盖全部 `htypes`。对于非 OHLCV 的自定义因子列，你"
"需要自己决定 `'last'` / `'mean'` 等聚合方式并写进 `agg`。"
msgstr ""
"Note: `resample()` requires `agg` to cover all `htypes`. For custom factor "
"columns that are not OHLCV, you need to decide the aggregation method yourself "
"(e.g., `'last'` / `'mean'`) and include it in `agg`."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:223
msgid "5.6 用 (M,L) mask 做 plot 高亮（事件日/信号日）"
msgstr "5.6 Use an (M, L) mask to highlight plots (event day / signal day)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:225
msgid ""
"在因子研究里，你经常会得到一个二维布尔矩阵 `mask_ml`，表示“每只股票在哪些日期满"
"足条件”（例如事件日、信号日、可交易池）。"
msgstr ""
"In factor research, you will often get a 2D boolean matrix `mask_ml`, "
"indicating “on which dates each stock meets the condition” (e.g., event dates, "
"signal dates, tradable universe)."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:227
msgid ""
"`HistoryPanel.plot()` 的 `highlight={'condition': mask_ml}` 支持直接把它映射到图"
"形中高亮点："
msgstr ""
"`HistoryPanel.plot()` with `highlight={'condition': mask_ml}` supports mapping "
"it directly onto the chart to highlight points:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:229
msgid ""
"若 `mask_ml.shape == (M_plot, L)`，其中 `M_plot` 为当前 `plot(shares=...)` 选中"
"的股票数，则按绘图 share 顺序对应；"
msgstr ""
"If `mask_ml.shape == (M_plot, L)`, where `M_plot` is the number of stocks "
"currently selected by `plot(shares=...)`, it corresponds in the plotting share "
"order;"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:230
msgid ""
"若 `mask_ml.shape == (M_all, L)`，其中 `M_all == len(hp.shares)`，则按 **share "
"名**抽取当前绘图子集（避免 silent 错行）；"
msgstr ""
"If `mask_ml.shape == (M_all, L)`, where `M_all == len(hp.shares)`, then extract "
"the current plotting subset by **share name** (to avoid silent row "
"misalignment);"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:231
msgid ""
"当 `layout='overlay'` 时默认 **primary-only** 显示高亮（与既有 Plotly highlight "
"语义一致）。"
msgstr ""
"When `layout='overlay'`, highlights are shown as **primary-only** by default "
"(consistent with existing Plotly highlight semantics)."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:247
msgid "5.4 Newey–West / Fama–MacBeth（背景：本节不实现）"
msgstr ""
"5.4 Newey–West / Fama–MacBeth (background: not implemented in this section)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:249
msgid ""
"在计量实证中，你可能会看到 **Newey–West（HAC）稳健标准误** 与 **Fama–MacBeth 两"
"步回归**。它们主要用于**回归推断**（标准误修正、风险溢价显著性检验），不属于 "
"`HistoryPanel.zscore()` 这类“基础变换”。 若需要发表级实证，建议将 "
"`HistoryPanel` 导出为 `DataFrame` 后使用 `statsmodels` 等工具完成推断流程。"
msgstr ""
"In empirical econometrics, you may see **Newey–West (HAC) robust standard "
"errors** and **Fama–MacBeth two-step regressions**. They are mainly used for "
"**regression inference** (standard error correction, significance tests for "
"risk premia), and are not “basic transformations” like `HistoryPanel.zscore()`. "
"If you need publication-grade empirical work, it’s recommended to export "
"`HistoryPanel` to a `DataFrame` and then use tools such as `statsmodels` to "
"complete the inference workflow."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:254
msgid "6. 使用 apply_ta 统一调用技术指标"
msgstr "6. Use apply_ta to call technical indicators in a unified way"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:256
msgid ""
"如果你已经熟悉 `qteasy.tafuncs` 或 ta-lib，可以通过 `HistoryPanel.apply_ta()` 做"
"统一封装："
msgstr ""
"If you are already familiar with `qteasy.tafuncs` or ta-lib, you can use "
"`HistoryPanel.apply_ta()` for a unified wrapper:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:269
msgid ""
"这样可以避免在循环中手动调用 `tafuncs.sma`，`HistoryPanel` 会自动对所有选定股票"
"广播计算。"
msgstr ""
"This avoids manually calling `tafuncs.sma` in a loop; `HistoryPanel` will "
"automatically broadcast the computation across all selected stocks."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:273
msgid "7. 识别蜡烛形态"
msgstr "7. Identify candlestick patterns"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:275
msgid ""
"对于 OHLC 数据，还可以通过 `HistoryPanel.candle_pattern()` 封装 ta-lib 的蜡烛形"
"态识别函数，例如："
msgstr ""
"For OHLC data, you can also wrap ta-lib’s candlestick pattern recognition "
"functions via `HistoryPanel.candle_pattern()`, for example:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:286
msgid "信号含义通常是："
msgstr "The signal meaning is usually:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:288
msgid "`0`：未识别到该形态；"
msgstr "`0`: the pattern is not detected;"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:289
msgid "正数 / 负数：不同方向或强度的形态信号（取决于具体 ta-lib 函数的定义）。"
msgstr ""
"Positive / negative values: pattern signals in different directions or with "
"different strengths (depending on the specific ta-lib function’s definition)."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:293
msgid "8. 生成研究用 bool 掩码（`where`）"
msgstr "8. Generate a research boolean mask (`where`)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:295
msgid ""
"面板 ``values`` 的轴顺序为 **(标的数 M, 时间长度 L, 指标列数 N)**，与 "
"``hp.shape`` 一致。``hp.where(condition)`` 返回 **同形** 的 ``numpy.ndarray``，"
"``dtype=bool``，且不修改 ``hp``。``cum_return``、``normalize``、``portfolio`` 已"
"支持 ``mask=hp.where(...)``（或与 ``where`` 同广播规则的 ``bool`` 数组）。研究向"
"语义与边界（路径断开、基准日无效、组合与基准关系等）以 API docstring 为准。"
msgstr ""
"The axis order of panel ``values`` is **(number of assets M, time length L, "
"number of indicator columns N)**, consistent with ``hp.shape``. "
"``hp.where(condition)`` returns a **same-shape** ``numpy.ndarray``, "
"``dtype=bool``, and does not modify ``hp``. ``cum_return``, ``normalize``, and "
"``portfolio`` already support ``mask=hp.where(...)`` (or a ``bool`` array with "
"the same broadcasting rules as ``where``). For research-oriented semantics and "
"edge cases (path breaks, invalid base dates, portfolio–benchmark relationships, "
"etc.), refer to the API docstring."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:297
msgid "**与整表数值比较**（与 ``hp.values > 阈值`` 等价）："
msgstr ""
"**Compare against the full table of values** (equivalent to ``hp.values > "
"threshold``):"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:307
msgid ""
"**按时间维打标**（例如某一列索引为「事件日」，沿所有 htype 复制；以下为示意，需"
"保证 ``cond_ml`` 形状为 ``(M, L)``）："
msgstr ""
"**Label along the time dimension** (e.g., if the index of a certain column is "
"an “event day”, replicate it across all htypes; the following is illustrative—"
"make sure ``cond_ml`` has shape ``(M, L)``):"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:317
msgid "**按收盘价列构造条件**（``callable`` 接收当前 ``HistoryPanel``）："
msgstr ""
"**Build conditions based on the close-price column** (the ``callable`` receives "
"the current ``HistoryPanel``):"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:324
msgid "**复合条件与缺失值**："
msgstr "**Composite conditions and missing values**:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:331
msgid ""
"**说明**：形状恰好为 ``(M, L)`` 的二维条件表示「每个 (标的, 日) 对所有指标列共用"
"同一布尔值」，库内会先扩展为 ``(M, L, 1)`` 再广播到 ``(M, L, N)``。一维 "
"``(M,)`` 或 ``(M, 1)`` 表示仅随标的变化，会展开为 ``(M, 1, 1)`` 再广播。更完整的"
"参数与异常说明见 [HistoryPanel API 参考](../api/HistoryPanel.rst) 中 ``where`` "
"一节。"
msgstr ""
"**Note**: A 2D condition with shape exactly ``(M, L)`` means “for each (asset, "
"date), all indicator columns share the same boolean value”. The library will "
"first expand it to ``(M, L, 1)`` and then broadcast to ``(M, L, N)``. A 1D "
"``(M,)`` or ``(M, 1)`` means it varies only by asset; it will be expanded to "
"``(M, 1, 1)`` and then broadcast. For more complete parameter and exception "
"notes, see the ``where`` section in [HistoryPanel API Reference](../api/"
"HistoryPanel.rst)."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:333
msgid "8.1 累计收益与归一化（`cum_return` / `normalize`）"
msgstr "8.1 Cumulative return and normalization (`cum_return` / `normalize`)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:335
msgid ""
"返回 **新** ``HistoryPanel``（不修改原面板），默认对解析后的 ``close`` 列计算；"
"输出列名为 ``cumret_<列名>``、``norm_<列名>``（与复权列 ``close|b`` 并存时，仍可"
"传 ``htypes=None``，列名仍为 ``cumret_close``）。可与掩码联用："
msgstr ""
"Returns a **new** ``HistoryPanel`` (does not modify the original panel). By "
"default, it is computed on the parsed ``close`` column; output column names are "
"``cumret_<column_name>`` and ``norm_<column_name>`` (when coexisting with the "
"adjusted-price column ``close|b``, you can still pass ``htypes=None``, and the "
"column name is still ``cumret_close``). Can be used together with a mask:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:343
msgid "8.2 组合聚合（`portfolio`）"
msgstr "8.2 Portfolio aggregation (`portfolio`)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:345
msgid ""
"研究向：沿 **标的维** 对指定列做等权或加权平均，返回 **新** ``HistoryPanel``"
"（``hdates`` 不变）。``mask=`` 与 ``where`` 同广播规则。无 ``groups`` 且指定 "
"``benchmark`` 时，**基准标的不参与**组合计算，仅用于 "
"``benchmark_output='tag_along'``（多一行基准曲线）或 ``'excess_only'``（输出 "
"``excess_<列名>``）。非账户回测、无交易成本。详见 API docstring。"
msgstr ""
"Research-oriented: take an equal-weighted or weighted average of specified "
"columns along the **asset dimension**, and return a **new** ``HistoryPanel`` "
"(``hdates`` unchanged). ``mask=`` follows the same broadcasting rules as "
"``where``. When there are no ``groups`` and a ``benchmark`` is specified, the "
"**benchmark asset does not participate** in the combination calculation; it is "
"only used for ``benchmark_output='tag_along'`` (one extra row for the benchmark "
"curve) or ``'excess_only'`` (output ``excess_<column name>``). Not an account "
"backtest; no transaction costs. See the API docstring for details."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:355
msgid "8.3 列属性、比较与 ``loc``（与 pandas 的差异简述）"
msgstr ""
"8.3 Column attributes, comparisons, and ``loc`` (a brief note on differences "
"from pandas)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:357
msgid ""
"**列属性（只读）**：列名为合法 Python 标识符时可用 ``hp.close``，等价 "
"``hp['close']``；含 ``|`` 的复权列名等须用方括号。赋值请统一 ``hp['col'] "
"= ...``。"
msgstr ""
"**Column attributes (read-only)**: when a column name is a valid Python "
"identifier, you can use ``hp.close``, equivalent to ``hp['close']``; adjusted-"
"price column names containing ``|`` and the like must use brackets. For "
"assignment, consistently use ``hp['col'] = ...``."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:358
msgid ""
"**比较**：``hp.close > hp.open``、``hp > 0`` 等得到 **``numpy.ndarray``（bool）"
"**，不是子 ``HistoryPanel``；全形掩码可写 ``hp.where(hp.close > 15)``。两侧均为"
"面板时须 ``shares``、``hdates`` 一致；两列比较时多为两个 **单列** 子面板。"
msgstr ""
"**Comparison**: expressions like ``hp.close > hp.open`` and ``hp > 0`` yield a "
"**``numpy.ndarray`` (bool)**, not a sub-``HistoryPanel``; a full-shape mask can "
"be written as ``hp.where(hp.close > 15)``. When both sides are panels, "
"``shares`` and ``hdates`` must match; when comparing two columns, it is usually "
"two **single-column** sub-panels."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:359
msgid ""
"**``loc``**：``hp.loc[s]`` 等价 ``hp[:, :, s]``，只沿 **时间（hdates）** 轴筛"
"选；**不要**把 ``where`` 得到的 ``(M, L, N)`` 掩码传给 ``loc``，格点条件仍用 "
"``where`` + 后续 ``mask=``。"
msgstr ""
"**``loc``**: ``hp.loc[s]`` is equivalent to ``hp[:, :, s]``; it filters only "
"along the **time (hdates)** axis. **Do not** pass the ``(M, L, N)`` mask "
"produced by ``where`` into ``loc``; grid-point conditions should still use "
"``where`` + a subsequent ``mask=``."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:361
msgid ""
"细节与边界情况以 [HistoryPanel API 参考](../api/HistoryPanel.rst) 为准（含 "
"``where``、``cum_return``、``normalize``、``portfolio``）。"
msgstr ""
"For details and edge cases, refer to the [HistoryPanel API Reference](../api/"
"HistoryPanel.rst) (including ``where``, ``cum_return``, ``normalize``, "
"``portfolio``)."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:371
msgid "9. 从 HistoryPanel 研究到 Strategy / Operator：迁移路径"
msgstr "9. From HistoryPanel research to Strategy / Operator: migration path"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:373
msgid ""
"`HistoryPanel` 上的 `cum_return`、`portfolio`、`plot` 等是**研究向**工具：便于肉"
"眼筛因子、看粗组合线，**不包含**交割周期、手续费、滑点、信号类型（PT/PS/VS）解析"
"等与正式回测一致的账户语义。结论若用于实盘或严肃评价，应把**同一经济含义**的规则"
"写进策略的 `realize()`，交给 `Operator` + Backtester。"
msgstr ""
"`cum_return`, `portfolio`, `plot`, etc. on `HistoryPanel` are **research-"
"oriented** tools: convenient for eyeballing factors and viewing rough portfolio "
"curves, and **do not include** account semantics consistent with formal "
"backtests, such as settlement cycles, fees, slippage, and parsing of signal "
"types (PT/PS/VS). If the conclusions are to be used for live trading or serious "
"evaluation, you should write rules with the **same economic meaning** into the "
"strategy’s `realize()`, and hand them to `Operator` + Backtester."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:375
msgid ""
"下面用**同一思想——20 期简单动量**串起两阶段（需本地已配置数据源并下载相应字段；"
"股票代码仅为示意）。"
msgstr ""
"Below, we use the **same idea—20-period simple momentum** to connect the two "
"stages (requires that a data source has been configured locally and the "
"corresponding fields have been downloaded; stock codes are for illustration "
"only)."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:377
msgid "9.1 研究阶段：在多标的 `HistoryPanel` 上算因子并粗看截面"
msgstr ""
"9.1 Research stage: compute factors on a multi-asset `HistoryPanel` and take a "
"quick look at cross-sections"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:404
msgid ""
"这里你在 **三维面板** 上完成了因子列生产、截面变换与粗聚合；若结果满意，进入 "
"9.2 把**因子定义**搬到策略里。"
msgstr ""
"Here you have completed factor-column generation, cross-sectional transforms, "
"and rough aggregation on a **3D panel**; if the results look good, proceed to "
"9.2 and move the **factor definition** into the strategy."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:406
msgid "9.2 正式回测阶段：`FactorSorter` + `Operator`"
msgstr "9.2 Formal backtesting stage: `FactorSorter` + `Operator`"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:408
msgid ""
"选股类策略常用 `FactorSorter`：`realize()` 返回**每个标的一个标量因子**（长度 = "
"股票数），框架再按 `max_sel_count`、`sort_ascending` 等做排序与权重。下面动量与 "
"9.1 中 `returns(..., periods=20)` 的经济含义一致，但数据来自策略窗口注入（与回测"
"步对齐、受 `use_latest_data_cycle` 等约束）。"
msgstr ""
"Stock-selection strategies commonly use `FactorSorter`: `realize()` returns "
"**one scalar factor per instrument** (length = number of stocks), and the "
"framework then sorts and assigns weights based on `max_sel_count`, "
"`sort_ascending`, etc. The momentum below has the same economic meaning as "
"`returns(..., periods=20)` in 9.1, but the data comes from injection via the "
"strategy window (aligned with backtest steps and constrained by "
"`use_latest_data_cycle`, etc.)."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:444
msgid "**注意**："
msgstr "**Note**:"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:446
msgid ""
"`Operator` 默认组内可使用 PT 类目标仓位信号；`FactorSorter` 与 PT 的搭配以你项目"
"中的策略文档为准。"
msgstr ""
"By default, `Operator` allows using PT-class target-position signals within "
"groups; how `FactorSorter` is paired with PT should follow the strategy "
"documentation in your project."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:447
msgid ""
"HP 里用全样本算的 rank/zscore，与回测中「每步仅见历史窗口」的因子可能略有数值差"
"异，属预期现象；应以策略内 `get_data` 为准复核防前视。"
msgstr ""
"Ranks/z-scores computed in HP using the full sample may differ slightly "
"numerically from factors in backtests where “each step only sees the historical "
"window”; this is expected. You should re-check using `get_data` inside the "
"strategy to guard against look-ahead bias."

