#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:480
msgid ""
"缺列或表未下载时，`get_history_data` 会报错；请先通过数据源教程补齐表数据。"
msgstr ""
"If a column is missing or a table has not been downloaded, `get_history_data` "
"will raise an error; please first complete the table data via the data source "
