#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:482
msgid "10.2 两块面板对齐后再派生（不同来源/不同拉取）"
msgstr ""
"10.2 Align two panels first, then derive (different sources / different pulls)"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:484
msgid ""
"``align_to`` 要求两侧 **``htypes`` 名称与顺序完全一致**。若你只分别拉取了 "
"``close`` 与 ``pb`` 两列，需先扩成同构列（缺失侧用 ``NaN`` 占位），对齐后再用 "
"``assign`` 把有效数值写回同一套列名："
msgstr ""
"``align_to`` requires that **the ``htypes`` names and order match exactly** on "
"both sides. If you only fetched the ``close`` and ``pb`` columns separately, "
"you need to first expand them into a homogeneous set of columns (use ``NaN`` as "
