msgstr ""
"At any step, you can easily switch back to a `DataFrame` to work together with "
"pandas / sklearn / statsmodels, etc.;"

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:581
msgid ""
"**正式回测**请通过 `Strategy.realize` + `Operator` 完成；研究向 HP 与回测引擎的"
"边界与迁移路径见 **§9**。"
msgstr ""
"For **formal backtesting**, use `Strategy.realize` + `Operator`; for the "
"boundary and migration path between research-oriented HP and the backtest "
"engine, see **§9**."

#: ../../source/tutorials/2.5-historypanel-data-analysis.md:583
